		Budgie Caffeine Applet is an addon for Budgie Desktop to prevent screen dimming (and lock screen) on long idle time.
		</p>
		<p>
		Features of the applet:
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Timer</li>
			<li>Notification</li>
